@startuml
skinparam shadowing false
skinparam backgroundColor white
skinparam defaultFontName "Microsoft YaHei"
skinparam roundcorner 10
skinparam state {
    BackgroundColor white
    BorderColor black
    BorderThickness 1.5
    FontColor black
    ArrowColor black
}
skinparam arrow {
    Color black
    Thickness 1
}
title 经验规则生命周期(新建 → 复测 → 采用决策)

' ===== 状态定义 =====
state "新建 / 未复核\n(unreviewed · watch)" as New
state "复测中\n(watching · 累积评估)" as Retesting
state "暂停采用\n(suspend)" as Suspend
state "继续复测\n(retest)" as Retest
state "修复证据\n(repair · needsFix)" as Repair
state "限制使用\n(limit)" as Limit
state "默认采用\n(adopt · validated)" as Adopt

[*] --> New : 规则提炼入库

New --> Retesting : 录入首次复测评估

' ===== 决策闸门(忠于 adoptionDecisionFor 的判定顺序)=====
' 1. suspend 优先
Retesting --> Suspend : 结论 conflicted / 维护回归未解 / 复测矩阵冲突阻断
' 2. retest(版本覆盖不足)
Retesting --> Retest : 修订后当前版本复测不足(版本覆盖未 covered)
' 3. repair(协议/证据缺口)
Retesting --> Repair : 协议执行阻断或不完整 / 证据缺口(qualityIssues>0)
' 4. retest(样本/矩阵不足)
Retesting --> Retest : 样本独立性弱 / 评估<2次 / insufficient / 矩阵未完成
' 5. limit
Retesting --> Limit : 槽位刚恢复 / 趋势走弱(declining)/ mixed 分歧
' 6. adopt(最严门槛,最后才到)
Retesting --> Adopt : supported 且 稳定分≥75 且 高置信
' supported 但门槛不足 → limit
Retesting --> Limit : supported 但置信或稳定分不足

' ===== 回流复测 =====
Retest --> Retesting : 补充独立复测样本
Repair --> Retesting : 补齐协议 / 场景证据后重测
Suspend --> Retesting : 收窄边界 / 拆分场景后恢复观察

' ===== 采用后的再评估回路 =====
Limit --> Retesting : 在已验证场景持续观察 / 新增评估
Adopt --> Retesting : 出现新冲突或趋势走弱触发复评

' ===== 终止 =====
Suspend --> [*] : 边界无法收敛 · 弃用
Adopt --> [*] : 稳定沉淀为默认行动参考

@enduml
